Package: Espiga
Title: Genomic Prediction Model Comparison
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c( person("Christian", "Escoto-Sandoval",
              email = "ces1405@illinois.edu",
              role  = c("aut", "cre")),
              person("Jessica", "Rutkoski",
              email = "jrut@illinois.edu",
              role  = "aut"))
Description: Fits and compares multiple regression and Bayesian models
    for genomic prediction using cross-validated RMSE as selection
    criterion. Includes CatBoost, XGBoost, Random Forest, PCR,
    Ridge, Lasso, Elastic Net, BayesA, BayesL, and BayesR.
